Name: Zombie Death Quota
About the game: Help Special Forces operative Della retrieve the Bio-waste containers that are causing the zombie outbreak and evacuate in the helicopter. Explore the island and find Bio-waste containers and neutralise enough Zombies to achieve the Zombie Death Quota. Scavenge for guns, ammo, grenades and health packs scattered around the island to help you in your mission. This first person shooter was first launched on the Xbox 360 Indie Games service in 2012, the XBLIG service was closed down in 2017. Play this part of gaming history which is preserved here today and support me by checking out my newest game Splodge Royale. Weapons Flamethrower: A Heavy Metal flamethrower. Levels Play 13 increasingly difficult levels.
